## API Routes

| Route | Method | Purpose |
|-------|--------|---------|
| `/api/lead` | POST | Capture lead → DB + email |
| `/api/contact` | POST | Same as `/api/lead`, semantic alias for contact page |
| `/api/health` | GET | Uptime check |

All routes return: `{ success: true, data: {...} }` or `{ success: false, error: "message" }`

